  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="4871443">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4871443/" class="title-link">实际上，遗老们要自圆其说自己的突然转变，是一...</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4871443"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/48251807/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/48251807/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Simon</span>
